name: Alpha-Monsters - Upper-case Monsters
description:
Spell out your little monsters name with these one of a kind Alpha-Monster Soft Letters.

Inspired by Jim Henson's Sesame Street letter monsters these cudly soft letters will brighten up any bedroom or playroom.

* Letters range from 18-28cm high (7-11 inches) 
* Made from reclaimed fabrics 
* Stuffed with Australian-made Allergy-free polyfill

There are no buttons, beads or anything harmful for baby so all Alpha-monsters are fine for infants.

CHOOSE FROM... 
Any letter of the alphabet 
Note: The colour and style of fabric used varies from letter to letter as I used up-cycled fabrics. If you want a specific colour please contact me or view my Etsy Store - jaffajaf.etsy.com

Request a specific colour by Contacting Me...

Want a whole alphabet? Sure thing - an entire alphabet is $150, please contact me to arrange your order.

name: Steggy's
description:
These are is a very cuddly Stegosaurus softies, with a row of multicoloured spines and a big swishy tale.

They is made from upcycled fabric with great texture and they extremely cuddly 

All my upcycled fabrics have been laudered in sensitive eco friendly washing powder. My toys are made in a pet and smoke free home. They are completely washable.

* Roughly 30cm high (12 inches)
* Stuffed with Australian-made Allergy-free polyfill.

Dionosaurs are amongst my favourite toys to design and make - great for boys or girls. Your little monster will be sure to love them.

name: Herringbone Owly
description:

All my upcycled fabrics have been laudered in sensitive eco friendly washing powder.

* Roughly 28cm high (11 inches)
* Made from Upcycled Fabric
* Stuffed with Australian-made Allergy-free polyfill

Each Owly is original and one of a kind. Your Owly may be slightly different than the ones in these pictures - with different coloured bellies, eyes or feet.
